{"tid":1511190,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"TVB 幕後開始做嘢？今集愛回家好似有啲嘢喎！","createTime":"2019-08-27T12:42:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-28T11:23:35.000Z","uid":301841,"like":12,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"d5998ea8a084685e3a3aa41be94c9ca968192a19","tid":1511190,"uid":301841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T12:42:02.000Z","msg":"起電視台幅牆度有「<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">香港人！振作吧！</span></span></strong>」字樣嘅海報<br />\n最後大四喜仲講咗：「大四喜，<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">缺一不可！</span></span></strong>」<br />\n係我諗多咗，定抑或TVB班幕後真係想暗地裡帶出啲訊息呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4677a9ad580edea75d8aba0e368617f3e1865aa1","tid":1511190,"uid":15696,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T12:43:08.000Z","msg":"唔好再睇"},{"pid":"dc14f4b0e7f51121bfe5f84d8ac891377d13c37b","tid":1511190,"uid":197393,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T12:43:09.000Z","msg":"諗多咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90ab6770c418c01637f448b860fbe982a4f31411","tid":1511190,"uid":175159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T12:44:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/df4Thbc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fdf4Thbc.png&h=22cd5054&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wEc9zXS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwEc9zXS.jpg&h=851d469e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9U7NmCS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9U7NmCS.jpg&h=b8bb220b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rBChJRd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrBChJRd.jpg&h=af19a575&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8oiwOhU.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8oiwOhU.png&h=6e017af5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"abf623d240568b63a1967c4dd6bf9fb53e5436a6","tid":1511190,"uid":140552,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T13:13:21.000Z","msg":"cctvb會唔奶共個機率低過零"},{"pid":"59ae6fb230758b8650a1dc5c39aae8046316dbf9","tid":1511190,"uid":54264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T11:23:35.000Z","msg":"無綫掀起白色恐怖，繼上周五(23/8)辭退近20名員工，當中涉及支持反《逃犯條例》的個人言論，包括字幕組、工程部、配音組、戲劇組成員及《愛．回家之開心速遞》的兩名編導和一名節目統籌。而無綫行政總裁李寶安當日解釋：「公司收入受本港市場不穩和政治動亂拖累，故需重整公司業務和精簡人手。」但有疑似當日遭TVB解僱的前員工在「連登」討論區發表一篇文章，開首便寫着：「我們是一群被辭職的TVB員工，今次好想同大家講，公司一直都存在着白色恐怖，希望各位留意及小心。」<br />\n<br />\n今日無綫政治打壓又有第二波，曾在無綫辦公室發聲，用五張memo紙寫上「黑白是良知」的監製李志倫（Jacky）今午亦被炒，連同組的3名同事，全組所屬的綜藝及戲劇製作部團隊全被「炒起」。《蘋果》今日聯絡Jacky，他以短訊回覆：「今日唔講住，多謝，有心喇。」他在下午四時許在facebook更新了一張高舉五隻手指，似暗示隻手遮天的黑白照片，明顯表達此刻個人心聲，不少人都留言叫他「加油」。<br />\n<br />\nJacky一向是余詠珊的心腹，近年為TVB立下不少功勞，製作不少大型節目，包括《回歸二十周年大匯演》、劇集《機動部隊》、《女人四十》、《爸爸的告白》等，其中《博愛歡樂傳萬家》更連續三年獲得博愛方面聯署讚賞。Jacky最近正籌備一個關於年輕人的電視電影，原計劃下月中開拍，但今午接到大信封，已即時被解僱。<br />\n<br />\n近月在逆權運動中，Jacky屢在網上表態支持，除將「黑白是良知」memo貼在辦公室的玻璃上，還有一張寫上「生人勿近」的白色紙倒貼在側邊，8月中時Jacky接受傳媒查詢時還表示不驚公司抽後算賬：「唔驚，公司內部總有真香港人、真香港老闆。」可惜最後仍難逃被炒命運。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20190828/59983111\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190828%2F59983111&d=hq0sVSmFYzKD%2BASQGeqgxstNvD6oN5AbUd1%2F%2Bp%2BoAYU%3D&h=585ccfeb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190828%2F59983111&h=18b21d5c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20190828/59983111</a>"}]}